Package: com.github.amkay.gradle.git.release.notes.dsl

[Groovy] Class GitReleaseNotesPluginExtension

    • com.github.amkay.gradle.git.release.notes.dsl.GitReleaseNotesPluginExtension

    • The Gradle plugin extension. This is the entry point of the DSL to configure the plugin.
